            <title>[GROOVY-2224] Groovy Console - Closing Frame with Find/Replace dialog open leaves the dialog open and process not ending</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-2224</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the Groovy Console, if the Find or Replace window is open and you close the frame, then the dialog remains visible and the process does not end. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This needs to be changed to close and dispose the dialog on exit. &lt;/p&gt;
</description>
